  "description": "Karplus-Strong everywhere. All 8 voices at high blend with K-S algorithm, character at 0.8 (clean string, no snare buzz). Long decay on all voices (0.6–0.85). The result is a tuned metallic string instrument played percussively — somewhere between a hammered dulcimer, a gamelan, and a synthesized zither. Not drums.",
